videos.description: ECU's Kentrell Barkley gets the offensive rebound and goes back up strong to tie the game again and send it into a third overtime.
videos.headline: Tough layup sends ECU to triple overtime

videos.description: With the game tied in triple-overtime, Tulane's Louis Dabney throws the long-distance lob to Melvin Frazier for the huge dunk and the foul to put the Green Wave up on ECU.
videos.headline: High-flying alley-oops are even more fun in triple-OT
